{"tid":2198510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光時手足月報 - 8月刊","createTime":"2020-09-11T11:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T11:50:33.000Z","uid":193127,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e19606ddb9691b07d3711aa975aa1a7b4a97d4c9","tid":2198510,"uid":193127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJ7P0m9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJ7P0m9.jpg&h=cd2b958d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足，<br />\n<br />\n總結8月直到呢刻，繼續封市不封關、原告變被告、壹傳媒大樓被搜查、陳彥琳死因研訊疑點重重、記者被拘捕被粗暴對待、大肚婆被粗暴推倒、巴士司機無故被捕、12位手足仍然下落不明⋯⋯灰心事真係唔想日日提，一切在心中。<br />\n<br />\n但係「住係香港地，我愛香港地，死下死下死下香港地」，點死都好，點無力都好，鬥長命先會贏！至少我哋有努力，而且日後會更努力。今次8月月報就請嚟少少ON9，又少少努力嘅光時小編阿T過嚟講幾句！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDn4Pfr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDn4Pfr.jpg&h=e052050f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真呀，跪求大家多啲留言，同我哋一眾小編展開瘋狂激烈討論！我哋真係好想應你機！！話說之前好多手足叫我哋入多啲唔同國家嘅靚貨，今次就一次過介紹3個國家畀你，拒絕某國貨無難度！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uy6hpON.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUy6hpON.jpg&h=11011a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4aBFm7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4aBFm7.jpg&h=a756441f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYq90m8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYq90m8.jpg&h=51a28c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我哋8月開始同 《醫管局員工陣線HAEA》同《教育同行陣線》合作，為佢哋嘅會員提供優惠。雖然能力有限折扣微薄，但都希望代表光時團隊嘅小小心意。嚟緊我哋會同更多組織合作，希望互惠互利，互相PROMOTE大家出宇宙，請大家密切留意！<br />\n<br />\n以下係光時8月數據，我哋會繼續努力：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jUKPft.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jUKPft.jpg&h=25021eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，自8月23日至今，12位手足已經被困中國深圳鹽田看守所17日，律師同家屬至今仍然未能夠同佢哋任何一位聯絡，生死未卜。希望大家follow《12港人關注組》嘅 Facebook（12港人關注組）同 Instagram（save12hkyouths），持續關注手足情況。<br />\n<br />\n天佑義人，#save12hkyouths。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><a href=\"https://www.hkongs.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkongs.com%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=a6e450f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkongs.com/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n長夜再黑，總有光時。<br />\n無論如何，堅持到底。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光時團隊"},{"pid":"a65957a706d9351dc6580daeeca6b45dc13688e9","tid":2198510,"uid":193127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1bfc744dbdd3e387ddde3881878069dbf630b5","tid":2198510,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e297e34113a410307336c0a3f1e74a925d5eaff","tid":2198510,"uid":2117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09d9ae6992843dbfea32c8667e849bfcf563072","tid":2198510,"uid":193127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58376e2232de6f3bde08c4e92697cc84a43c6991","tid":2198510,"uid":193127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr